   - `presentation.metadata`
   - `presentation.design_system`
   - `presentation.slides[]`

2. **DESIGN_SYSTEM_SUMMARY**: Quick reference for colors/fonts

3. **COT_DECISION_SUMMARY**: Design decisions to honor
```

## Standalone Mode

Provide a valid JSON slide specification following this schema:

```json
{
  "presentation": {
    "metadata": {
      "title": "string",
      "subtitle": "string",
      "author": "string",
      "date": "string"
    },
    "design_system": {
      "color_palette": {
        "primary": "#hex",
        "secondary": "#hex",
        "accent": "#hex",
        "text_dark": "#hex",
        "text_light": "#hex",
        "background": "#hex"
      },
      "typography": {
        "title_font": "string",
        "body_font": "string"
      }
    },
    "slides": [
      {
        "slide_number": 1,
        "type": "string",
        "layout_template": "string",
        "title": { "text": "string" },
        "content_blocks": [],
        "visual_elements": [],
        "speaker_notes": { "text": "string" }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

